cat << EOF
Gecko Media Player is a browser plugin that uses GNOME MPlayer to play media
in a browser. It should work with all browsers on Unix-ish systems (Linux,
BSD, and Solaris), that use the NS4 API (Mozilla, Firefox, Opera, etc.).
EOF
